<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="//maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" id="bootstrap-css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styleLogin.css">
    <title>Asela</title>
</head>


<body class="form-v4">
	<div class="page-content">
		<div class="form-v4-content">
			<div class="form-left">
				<h2>Association sauve et les animaux</h2>
				<p class="text-1">Si vous êtes bénévole pour l'association sauve et les animaux vous pouvez vous connecter !</p>
                
				<p class="text-2"><span>Si vous n'êtes pas bénévole:</span> <br>
                Vous vous êtes perdu ! <br>
                Revenez sur notre site en <a href="http://localhost:4040/v1/home" style="color: white; text-decoration: underline; font-weight: 800;">cliquant ICI.</a></p>
			</div>
			<form class="form-detail" name="myForm" action="#" method="post" id="myform">
				<h2>Se connecter</h2>
          
        <div id="errorDiv"><span class="error" id="errorname"></span></div>
         
          <div class="form-group">
          <div class="form-row col-md-6">
            <label for="your_email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" name="userEmail" autocomplete="userEmail" class="input-text" id="loginEmail" aria-describedby="basic-addon3" required>
          </div>
            <div class="form-row col-md-6">
              <label for="userPassword">Mot de passe</label>
              <input type="password"  autocomplete="userPassword" name="userPassword" id="loginPwd" class="input-text" required>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="form-row-last">
            <input type="button" class="login" value="Se connecter" id="button">
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.11.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/jquery.validation/1.16.0/jquery.validate.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/jquery.validation/1.16.0/additional-methods.min.js"></script>
   
    
  </body>
  </html>
  
